---
title: One-Pan Mushroom Cauliflower “Risotto” with Parmesan & Thyme
description: What’s saucy and a little cheesy? The answer: This dish right here (not your tipsy uncle at Thanksgiving)! Our clever chefs created a grain-free take on risotto using cauliflower rice and packed it with triple the mushroom flavor. They cook the “risotto” with deeply-flavored mushroom stock and browned mushrooms, sprinkle it with truffle zest, then finish the bowl with more browned mushrooms. It’s mushroom mania in the best way possible.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-mushroom-cauliflower-risotto-4b825647.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-mushroom-cauliflower-risotto-61b0d494dc99e760b66ccdf5-16783939.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-mushroom-cauliflower-risotto-61b0d494dc99e760b66ccdf5
nutrition:
  calories: 450 kcal
